metadata.dc:description: Authors present a case report of an aneurysm from Posterior Tibial artery secondary to a traffic accident with trauma on tibia and perone. First symptoms appeared four months after accident.
metadata.dc:title: Complicación vascular tardía tras fractura de tibia y peroné.
[Late vascular complication after fracture of tibia and fibula].
